1 ) Login with ssh on sever
CMD : ssh root@192.168.1.52

2 ) Django Clone from GIT or SVN
CMD : git clone https://github.com/Sachin880699/bootie-shoes-django-backend-with-api

3 ) need to create virtualenv 
CMD : python3 -m venv env_name

4 ) Activate virtualenv
CMD : cd env_name/bin && source activate

5 ) install screen
CMD : sudo apt install screen

6 ) Then Run Development server
CMD : screen -d -m python manage.py runserver 192.168.1.52:8000

7 ) Now you can access django server by ( 192.168.1.52:8000 ) IP
